            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"280\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/SEyTNn0PbSoxQCUHdryjbw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUzOA--/https://media.zenfs.com/vi/the_bamboo_works_186/56887ded16464727b86a3c32b16bcb9d\" width=\"500\"/></div></figure></div>",
